<td style="text-align:right;font-size:115%;padding-top: 0.6em;">
<div class="plainlinks hlist navbar mini">
<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="/wiki/Template:Politics_of_Canada" title="Template:Politics of Canada"><span title="View this template">v</span></a></li>
